  "description": "<p><strong>Position title : Sales Executive( Retail Sales)</strong></p><p>Location: Jalan Besar</p><p>Working Days: 5.5 days a week (Must be able to work on weekends)</p><p>Working hours : 11am to 9pm</p><p>Salary : $3,100 basic+ Comm<br /></p><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Candidate with <strong>retail or jewellery experience</strong> is an added advantage</li><li>Minimum GCE “N” level</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Understand and be able to explain to customers the range of Jewelley the company has to offer</li><li>Promote the various products, services and schemes to customers</li><li>Attend to customers and ensure service delivery standards are met in achieving total customer satisfaction</li><li>Achieve monthly sales targets.</li><li>Ensure merchandise and displays are consistently well presented and displayed</li><li>Manage and maintain the overall positive image of the showroom</li><li></li></ul><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p><p></p>",
